---
title: Cheesy Beyond Meat® Taquitos with Zesty Guacamole
description: Taquitos are a traditional Mexican street food that is typically deep-fried. We’ve baked ours instead, for a healthier twist! They crisp up beautifully in the oven, while the cheesy Beyond Meat® centre melts to perfection.

